reviews.text: a pretty good shopping mall! (my review is duplicated by the Chinese one.)
It might look new and old but hell do you get a great view over the racecourse

Nice shopping mall in Fo Tan, relatively close to the MTR. This is in a more luxurious housing development as well, so you can get more expensive, high-quality groceries here. The extra space also makes this place feel more luxurious than an equivalent place close to Central or TST.
It's not a bad little mall. A few places to eat and a good supermarket.
